    "Quantumsecure hash functions can provide data integrity and authentication.",
    "They remain secure against quantum attacks, thus enhancing data integrity in FedFM [311].",
    "Quantum homomorphic encryption allows computations on encrypted data without decryption.",
    "It can offer privacy protection on transmitted model parameters during the collaborative learning effort in FedFM [312].",
